.IP "\&.RS [ \*Vi\*O ]"
Shifts the left margin to the right (relatively) the amount of \*Vi\*O ens. The
\*L\&.RS\*O
macro calls can be nested up to nine levels.  If \*Vi\*O is not specified for
the first
\*L\&.RS\*O
call, the relative right shift increases \&.5 inch for
\*Lnroff\*O
and four picas for
\*L*troff\*O
text formatters.
Nested
\*L\&.RS\*O
calls increment the relative indent by \*Vi\*O ens, or by \&.2 inch for
\*Lnroff\*O,
or by 2 picas for
\*L*troff\*O
